40.comment: Murray was bottled up early on, but broke free for a 34-yard burst following intermission. Murray tallied 95 yards and 2 touchdowns on 15 carries. He and McKinnon were just 1 carry apart, but Murray outgained his teammate by a wide margin; McKinnon was limited to 48 yards.
